# fmc_ikev2_ipsec_proposals (Data Source)

This data source reads the IKEv2 IPsec Proposals.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "fmc_ikev2_ipsec_proposals" "example" {
  items = {
    "my_ikev2_ipsec_proposals" = {
    }
  }
}
```
